  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK2">
<l>kaṟṟataṉā lāya payaṉeṉkol, vālaṟiva</l>
<l>ṉaṟṟā ṭoḻāa reṉiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What Profit have those derived from learning, who worship not the good feet of Him who is possessed of pure knowledge ?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <p>
(i - ḷ). ellā nūlkaḷaiyuṅ kaṟṟavark kakkalviyaṟivāṉāya payaṉ yātu, meyyuṇarviṉai yuṭaiyāṉatu nalla tāḷkaḷait toḻārāyiṉ, (e-ṟu).
        </p>
        <p>
evaṉeṉṉum viṉāppeyar eṉṉeṉṟāy īṇṭiṉmai kuṟittu niṉṟatu. kolleṉpa tacainilai. piṟavippiṇikku maruntākaliṉ ‘naṟṟāḷ’ eṉṟār ākam vaṟiviṟkuppayaṉ avaṉṟāḷait toḻutu piṟavi yaṟuttaveṉpatu itaṉāṟ cūṟappaṭṭatu.
        </p>
    </body>
  </text>
